{"tid":1723644,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG之城]有無人呢期都成日口淡淡作嘔反胃","createTime":"2019-11-15T08:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T14:46:34.000Z","uid":2625,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3768ed415a43c9c76a4852f75ac17eb10afa5756","tid":1723644,"uid":2625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:48:21.000Z","msg":"因為立場哥哥，相信好多人最近都聽過二噁英有幾恐怖。而呢單野爆出前好多前線手足都有表示過出紅疹，係咁肚屙，絲打就黎黑M 等等...<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/jtvKFg8.jpg[/img］\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjtvKFg8.jpg%5B%2Fimg%EF%BC%BD&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=4ee981a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/jtvKFg8.jpg[/img］</a><br />\n<br />\n依家班POPO癲到十八區係咁放，到底TG會殘留社區幾耐、飄去邊根本無人知，依家d空氣污染成點又係無人知，我地既食物同水會唔會都悄悄受到污染邊個知？<br />\n<br />\n近呢個月keep住無啦啦反胃又無野嘔，我想知有無其他人都有咁既情況，留個正皮比我，又或者其他巴絲身體有無咩奇怪症狀都可以講講<br />\n<br />\n利申：弱弱文宣和理非<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/XKqnrTK.jpg[/img］\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXKqnrTK.jpg%5B%2Fimg%EF%BC%BD&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=ef06df45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/XKqnrTK.jpg[/img］</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PCgYKKv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPCgYKKv.png&h=00f41582&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1af5bf5faee48b231bbd4b9e8c6d1b708b9ffa6e","tid":1723644,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:50:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67rehV1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67rehV1.jpg&h=1f4d5a27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fdb7968d17c7d618f4a3a933795c72cb39e74fb9","tid":1723644,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:52:08.000Z","msg":"我手生紅點，經常反胃，嘔口水"},{"pid":"67ee07a44935f9e46c8f2f647de063080a41cc33","tid":1723644,"uid":2625,"like":0,"dislike":0